{"tid":1758200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位民主派泛民議員，你地1月1先上任，唔該你地諗真D PLAN好D 之後要為人民做嘅野!","createTime":"2019-11-27T02:09:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T13:05:54.000Z","uid":74778,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"618834c02005e7f92e86a49e71005b94df551278","tid":1758200,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:09:54.000Z","msg":"<strong>你地所得嘅每一票都有血有淚，係香港人用條命換返黎!<br />\n<br />\n今次嘅全民覺醒，係勝利，亦都係新挑戰嘅開始！<br />\n喺無大台之下，民主派全面入主區議會，下一步立法會，直接威脅中央喺香港大小議會嘅影響力。中央一定無所不用其極咁修例、DQ、搬龍門、分化... 再同中央玩贏賬面數，佢一搬龍門真係可以乜都無<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地真係要無比咁團結，去建構黃色經濟圈，真正和勇不分。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">由區議員帶頭，成立基金！資援前線手足！香港係佢地打返黎嫁！</span><br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求，缺一不可!<br />\n團結香港，和勇不分!</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求係首要! 但最終目標係真正和勇不分，同建制完全割蓆，唔再對對面有任何依賴! <strong>真正黃色經濟圈!</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求:</span></span></strong><br />\n即刻要林鄭下台無可能，亦都無必要。佢做到成pat屎咁，中共想佢落台之前做多幾次醜人，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地都一樣逼到佢咁做！我地要逼到佢做我地嘅醜人！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一樣！<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">一定係清算黑警！</span></strong>獨立調查委員會，由大法官吹雞，調查6月9日至今<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>所有</strong></span>黑警執勤、當值、調查、扣留巿民、同黑社會組織關係等，<br />\n是否合法、<br />\n有否濫捕、<br />\n有否濫用私刑、<br />\n有否非謀殺、<br />\n有否非法處理屍體(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咸左)<br />\n是否違反人道守則！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n特赦所有手足！<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">6月9至今所有被捕人士都要得到公平審理！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正式撤回逃犯引導條例，雖然已經做左，但<strong>立法係建基於大多數民眾利益</strong>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">政府必須承諾以後<strong>行政立法司法</strong>，都必須以香港人權利為首要考慮及出發點!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而社會因為政府6月9日至10月23日(共137日)堅持唔肯撤回逃犯引導條例而出現嚴重撕裂，大量人命傷亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">特區政府必須負上全部責任!</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n制定真普選時間表!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">和勇不分，建構黃色經濟圈</span></span></strong><br />\n今次民主派，泛民所得嘅每一票，都係全香港，不分和勇，用條命去激起全民覺醒咁換返黎!<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">由區議員帶頭，成立基金！資援前線手足！</span>可以安撫人心，而且宜家香港人為社運搞眾籌唔係難事，仲要係幫助一D為香港流血嘅手足!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最終目標係真正和勇不分，同建制完全割蓆，唔再對對面有任何依賴! <strong>建構真正黃色經濟圈!</strong><br />\n<br />\n例如:<br />\nTecky Academy決定將全額資助因社運而被捕的人士報讀「人工智能及程式設計微學位」，希望有助各位於日後留港／外地發展。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/tecky.io/photos/a.1242620759210318/1553069384832119?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftecky.io%2Fphotos%2Fa.1242620759210318%2F1553069384832119%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=7537bb0c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/tecky.io/photos/a.1242620759210318/1553069384832119?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n利，從未聽過呢間野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">做住先！唔該！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">之後嘅路只能寄望民主派當選議員唔好再分化分裂，真係做返d巿民想做嘅野!!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c3ad81d1faf6c8e7a4a19587cd2a963844d72145","tid":1758200,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:12:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QWeEy2B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQWeEy2B.png&h=90138a27&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgsiPAW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfgsiPAW.png&h=78ef3435&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n怕香港人善忘嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n想聲援理大手足嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n和理非嘅，推行動post 啦<br />\n勇武嘅，推行動 post 啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個係行動post，星期三晚，我地聚首商場，以和理非聲援理大手足<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756593\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756593</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ffc4727e9935aaa36cc2e798c872ad40aa1f99cd","tid":1758200,"uid":321238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:13:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇智者諗到可以令黃絲攞足特首選委嗰600票？</span></span>"},{"pid":"314a37b9b2d218356794be4a413909fc5798267f","tid":1758200,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffc4727e9935aaa36cc2e798c872ad40aa1f99cd","tid":1758200,"uid":321238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T02:13:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有冇智者諗到可以令黃絲攞足特首選委嗰600票？</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"reply